As shaman pk, you won't get the really good abilities until much later. My advice would be to level till 34 before attempting the pvp role. 34 brings the pet, as well as a new DOT (you'll be using the low level ones for quite a while). With the alts and gear these days, your best bet would be to find a monk, and stick to him/her like glue until the levels mentioned above...or even longer. With a monk, resist buff him and you (magic most important), and always slow. Other than that, keep him/her healed and that is your tank. Through a root in on attacker if it sticks, and stay sowed. About all the advice i can give...only 30 shaman on Vallon atm, but 55 on blue server. (49 will be a very happy spell level)

